    dc:description "FIGURES 90–94. Pseudachorutes polychaetosus Gao & Palacios-Vargas (90–93) and P. longisetis Yosii (94): 90, chaetotaxy of head and Th. I–III; 91, chaetotaxy of Abd. III–VI; 92, labium; 93, tip of macroseta; 94, labium. Scales: Figs 90–91 = 0.1 mm, 92–94 = 0.01 mm." ;
